trans-unit.source: Defines an activity delegate with one in argument of type <c>T</c> and one out argument of type <c>TResult</c>.
trans-unit.target: 定義具有一個型別 <c>T</c> 之 in 引數和一個型別 <c>TResult</c> 之 out 引數的活動委派。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Activities.ActivityDelegate> enables activity authors to expose callbacks with specific signatures that users of the activity can provide activity-based handlers for.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Activities.ActivityDelegate> 可讓活動作者使用特定的簽章以公開回呼，活動使用者可據此提供活動處理常式。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Activities.ActivityFunc%6013> is an <xref:System.Activities.ActivityDelegate> that returns a value.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Activities.ActivityFunc%6013> 是 <xref:System.Activities.ActivityDelegate>，可傳回值。

trans-unit.source: The signature of the <xref:System.Activities.ActivityFunc%6013> is specified as generic type arguments.
trans-unit.target: 將 <xref:System.Activities.ActivityFunc%6013> 的簽章指定為泛型型別引數。

trans-unit.source: There are multiple generic versions of this type that take from 1 to 16 in arguments, plus the `out` argument, for the activity that is called.
trans-unit.target: 有多個泛型版本的此類型，取自 1 至 16 引數中加上`out`引數，稱為 「 活動。

trans-unit.source: There are also **ActivityAction** types for activity delegates that do not return values.
trans-unit.target: 另外還有**ActivityAction**不會傳回值的活動委派的類型。

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Activities.ActivityFunc`13" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 建立 <see cref="T:System.Activities.ActivityFunc`13" /> 類別的新執行個體。
